<lb n="1"/>  <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">بسم</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">اللّه</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">الرّحمن</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">الرّحيم</supplied> 
<lb n="2"/>  أدّى <gap reason="illegible" precision="low" extent="3"/> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">عـ</supplied>ـمّـ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ـا</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">يجب</supplied> عليه 
<lb n="3"/>  من الخراج بـ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ـههية</unclear> دينار 
<lb n="4"/>  لسنة ثلاث وثلثين 
<lb n="5"/>  وثلثمائة وكتب 
<lb n="6"/>  محمّد بن جعفر بخطّه 
</ab></div>
         <div type="edition"><ab>
 <lb n="1"/>bi smi ăl lāhi ăr raḥmāni ăr raḥīmi 
 <lb n="2"/>ʾaddà *** ʿammā yaǧibu ʿalay hi 
 <lb n="3"/>mina ăl ḫarāǧi bi hihyaẗa dīnār 
 <lb n="4"/>li sanaẗi ṯalāṯ:in wa ṯalāṯīna 
 <lb n="5"/>wa ṯalāṯi miʾaẗ:in wa kataba 
 <lb n="6"/>muḥammadu bnu ǧaʿfara bi ḫaṭṭi hi 
  </ab></div>
<div type="translation"><ab>
			<lb n="1"/>
		[Im Namen Gottes, des Barmherzigen und sich Erbarmenden!]
			<lb n="2"/>
		Es bezahlte [...... von] de[m, was] ihm [obliegt]
			<lb n="3"/>
		von der Grundsteuer in Hiyah (?) einen Dinar
			<lb n="4"/>
		für das Jahr dreihundert-
			<lb n="5"/>
		dreihundertdreißig. Es schrieb (dies)
			<lb n="6"/>
		Muḥammad ibn Ğaʿfar eigenhändig.
</ab></div>
